= SecureDrop =
SecureDrop is another widely used whistle-blowing platform installed at many news organizations. To set it up please refer to the official guide at <ref>https://github.com/freedomofpress/securedrop/blob/develop/docs/install.md</ref>. To use SecureDrop as a source check <ref>https://github.com/freedomofpress/securedrop/blob/develop/docs/source_user_manual.md</ref> and for using SecureDrop as a journalist refer to <ref>https://github.com/freedomofpress/securedrop/blob/develop/docs/journalist_user_manual.md</ref>. For general information and project code go to their main Github page <ref>https://github.com/freedomofpress/securedrop</ref>.

If you are a news or whistle-blowing site operator you may be interested in having your Hidden Service address listed in the Freedom of The Press Foundation's list <ref>https://freedom.press/securedrop/directory</ref>.

= Sparkleshare =
